title: Facebook Business Suite (Pages Manager)
description:
With Facebook Business Suite (Pages Manager), you can access and manage the tools your business needs to thrive across your Facebook Page and Instagram account, simplified and in one place. 

Use this app to: 
• Create, schedule, and manage posts and stories to your Facebook Page and Instagram account
• View all messages, comments, and activity that need your attention, so you can easily respond to customers
• See what's working with insights about your audience, so you know how your Facebook Page and Instagram account are doing
• Stay focused on what matters with notifications about important activity
